com.sun.enterprise.mgmt
Class ClusterView

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.enterprise.mgmt.ClusterView

public class ClusterView
extends java.lang.Object

ClusterView is a snapshot of the current membership of the group. The ClusterView is created anew each time a membership change occurs in the group. ClusterView is managed by ClusterViewManager.
